                <h1>Is Hollister Owned by Abercrombie? Discover the Connection!</h1>
                <p>Hollister Co. is indeed owned by Abercrombie & Fitch Co. Established in 2000, Hollister was created to capture the casual vibe of Southern California and appeal mainly to a younger audience. As a part of Abercrombie's brand portfolio, Hollister reflects the company's commitment to lifestyle-oriented fashion.</p>
